    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[展开与收起插件]]></title>
      <url>/2017/08/02/%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%8E%E6%94%B6%E8%B5%B7%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="为什么要写这个插件？"><a href="#为什么要写这个插件？" class="headerlink" title="为什么要写这个插件？"></a>为什么要写这个插件？</h3><p>最近一直在做公司代码优化方面的事情，由于公司页面中有很多地方都采用了展开与收起的效果（严格上来说，只是显示和隐藏，根本没有做任何动画效果），并且每个页面都是单独写一个的，没有统一，而且经过很多人的迭代之后，代码写都都不太一样，维护难度很高，看着也很不舒服，于是写了一个展开与收起插件，用来管理所有该效果，这样代码量也少了，而且维护成本大大降低，今后要再写类似效果，直接调用插件即可，只需要传入几个给定的配置项。</p>
<h3 id="需求分析"><a href="#需求分析" class="headerlink" title="需求分析"></a>需求分析</h3><p>编写该插件时，主要的效果就是，当点击展开按钮时，内容全部展开，再点击时，内容收起。实现比较简单。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="插件配置项"><a href="#插件配置项" class="headerlink" title="插件配置项"></a>插件配置项</h3><p>该插件主要存在以下几个配置项</p>
<ol>
<li>height: number类型，表示需要隐藏的内容的高度，默认为0</li>
<li>target: jquery类型，表示需要将内容展开与收起的对象</li>
<li>animation: boolean类型，表示展开与收起操作是否需要动画，默认为true</li>
<li>clickHandler: function类型，表示点击后的操作。</li>
<li>interval: number类型，表示动画时长。<h3 id="插件代码："><a href="#插件代码：" class="headerlink" title="插件代码："></a>插件代码：</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/**</div><div class="line"> * openUpAndClose: 该插件是展开与收起的插件，主要用于内容的展开与收起</div><div class="line"> * @param  options: object类型，是一个配置对象，主要有以下几个配置项</div><div class="line"> * 1. height: number类型，表示需要隐藏的内容的高度，默认为0</div><div class="line"> * 2. target: jquery类型，表示需要将内容展开与收起的对象</div><div class="line"> * 3. animation: boolean类型，表示展开与收起操作是否需要动画，默认为true</div><div class="line"> * 4. clickHandler: function类型，表示点击后的操作。</div><div class="line"> * 5. interval: number类型，表示动画时长。</div><div class="line"> * @return &#123;[type]&#125;         [description]</div><div class="line"> */</div><div class="line">$.fn.openUpAndClose = function (options) &#123;</div><div class="line">	if (typeof options !== &apos;object&apos; || !options) &#123;</div><div class="line">		options = &#123;&#125;;</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	var defaults = &#123;</div><div class="line">		height : 0,</div><div class="line">		target : this,</div><div class="line">		animation : true,</div><div class="line">		interval : 100,</div><div class="line">		clickHander : $.noop</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	var settings = $.extend(&#123;&#125; , defaults , options);</div><div class="line">	var target = settings.target;</div><div class="line">	settings.originalHeight = target.outerHeight();</div><div class="line">	if (settings.originalHeight &lt;= settings.height) &#123;</div><div class="line">		this.remove();</div><div class="line">		return;</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	settings.isShow = false;</div><div class="line">	target.css(&#123;</div><div class="line">		height : settings.height,</div><div class="line">		overflow : &apos;hidden&apos;</div><div class="line">	&#125;);</div><div class="line">	return this.each(function () &#123;</div><div class="line">		var $this = $(this);</div><div class="line">		$this.on(&apos;click&apos; , function () &#123;</div><div class="line">			if (!settings.isShow) &#123;</div><div class="line">				if (settings.animation) &#123;</div><div class="line">					target.animate(&#123;</div><div class="line">						height : settings.originalHeight,</div><div class="line">						overflow : &apos;auto&apos;</div><div class="line">					&#125; , settings.interval);</div><div class="line">				&#125; else &#123;</div><div class="line">					target.css(&#123;</div><div class="line">						height : &apos;auto&apos;</div><div class="line">					&#125;);</div><div class="line">				&#125;;</div><div class="line">				settings.isShow = true;</div><div class="line">			&#125; else &#123;</div><div class="line">				if (settings.animation) &#123;</div><div class="line">					target.animate(&#123;</div><div class="line">						height : settings.height,</div><div class="line">						overflow : &apos;hidden&apos;</div><div class="line">					&#125; , settings.interval);</div><div class="line">				&#125; else &#123;</div><div class="line">					target.css(&#123;</div><div class="line">						height : settings.height + &apos;px&apos;</div><div class="line">					&#125;);</div><div class="line">				&#125;</div><div class="line">				settings.isShow = false;</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			settings.clickHander.call(this , settings);</div><div class="line">		&#125;)</div><div class="line">	&#125;)</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
      
        
